com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.model

Interface IBMECMSyncItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IBMECMBaseObject>, IBMECMBaseObject, Serializable

    public interface IBMECMSyncItem
extends IBMECMBaseObject
    Represents an item that has been enabled for syncing.

    A list of sync items can be retrieved by calling IBMECMDesktop.retrieveSyncItems().
